<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Greenland vuk gam apat leh, India gam apatin,
 Africa gam haksa leh, gam dang tamtak apat;
 Luilien panga chengte, leh tang leh phai a miten,
 Gitloh hatkawl apat a, Hukdawk di'n ei sam ui.

[V2]
 2. Silon tuikuol nuom chungah, huihchim pha a hung nung,
 Etna mun cheng a hawih a, mihing mai a gilo;
 Pathien thilpiek simsen loh, changin a um ngal un,
 Mahleh Pathien helo ten Thing, Suong bul a ho ui.

[V3]
 3. Eihaw chunglam chitna a Thagau hihvak sate'n,
 Vakna pie lo ding I him, thim laka chengte chuh?
 Hukdamna! Aw hukdamna, kiko pih zel unla,
 Lei gam tawpa chengte'n le, Messia min a het na'n.

[V4]
 4. Huih nungin A thu tawk un, tui luong inle tawk un,
 Tuisuohgiet lien tak banga, gamtin a luoh suok ma'n;
 Belam No gilote ding-a thi chuh hungtun ma'n,
 Tanpa, Lalpen, leh Siempa, Panpih in na pang un.</lyrics>
<title>FROM GREENLAND'S ICY MOUNTAINS</title>
<hymn_number>259</hymn_number>
</song>